<br>
How to switch statues : <br>
Method #1 : Convince the heirarchy of the temple to switch the statues for you.<br>
1) Determine if the statue is indeed a golem.  If so, can you dispell it without having it activate and change poses?  If so, do so. If not, the convince the priesthood scam will probably not work.  Remember that a simple detect magic coming up positive is no guarantee it is a golem.  It could just be blessed, protected from pigeons, or some other such effect.<br>
