2) Arrange to have your beautiful statue shrunk (1st level spell, growth, reversed) to a small enough size that it can be carried while you teleport.  A 9th level wizard casting it will shrink an item to 1/10 its normal dimensions, or 1/1000 its normal mass. (a twice man sized statue, 12 feet tall, about 6400 lb, will reduce to one 1.2 feet tall and about 6.4 lb) and will stay shrunk for 45 rounds.<br>
